{"tid":390103,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［地獄黑仔王求求攵］錯手刪Whatsapp","createTime":"2017-09-06T20:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T01:34:02.000Z","uid":97738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f705443fa23cf61c713432acf445b178fa35c3f7","tid":390103,"uid":97738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T20:47:52.000Z","msg":"搞左7個幾鐘都整唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n手殘刪左whatsapp，backup原本有5gb幾，Restore backup時見佢話&quot;your media will be restore in the background&quot;，但restore完啲media變哂問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟手㩒錯iCloud backup多次，得返1gb多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲record好似overwrite咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲知道啲media點restore返同iCloud可唔可以拎返之前個record出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d040a716896c071bda6c18c50c04577fcde9f4","tid":390103,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T21:44:01.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f52afd715fe8f08ea9935d66c6e868d2c3cf16","tid":390103,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T22:24:19.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"f677b494905773c89f710bca2c3ddd00409b2145","tid":390103,"uid":97738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:47:15.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbd78c9de57fe04409aac3ce31829118000cdcf","tid":390103,"uid":58999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"You are done"},{"pid":"dd1d1d83d63049e933ddd79a5d804d950627a62c","tid":390103,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"樓主正一柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ef9b418585baf6ea82b62a994ac7b2db3d3321","tid":390103,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:56:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"841d7403fc2efbca51857cd67a5038d5365a6511","tid":390103,"uid":18865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"iphone 自己個 backup 同 whatsapp 內置個 backup 放係 icloud 唔同位置<br />\n<br />\n如果你係 overwrite 咗 whatsapp 個內置 backup，你 check 下你 iphone 個 backup 係唔係度，有嘅話你可以考慮重設成部 iphone 再 install 過，都會有返 whatsapp d history<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"b5579dea4353735a599581e079e7817aa92ebfbc","tid":390103,"uid":18865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/092914_3cb7c0399fc7ae32946707a75bc5e360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F092914_3cb7c0399fc7ae32946707a75bc5e360.jpg&h=d0a9b6ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係 iphone 嘅 backup，要成部機重設之後先可以 restore 嘅 backup<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/092948_7b416dae29083f7afc5ea0c194d3efd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F092948_7b416dae29083f7afc5ea0c194d3efd3.jpg&h=5f4de706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻係 whatsapp 嘅內置 backup，刪咗 whatsapp 再裝返就可以 restore 嘅 backup<br />\n<br />\n兩個 backup 獨立的<br />\n你 check 下你 iphone 個 last backup 係幾時，再考慮下會唔會重設手機<br />\n<br />\n利申：9 up，重咩事都有風險"}]}